If list order may be changed, or new items may be added, you should add wx:key to make items unique, by this the state of each items will be kept.
wx:key supports two types of value:

String, which is some property name of item in wx:for loop. This property value must be unique String or Number, and must not be changed dynamically.

this, which could be used when items themselves are unique String or Number.


